<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230258>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A – C: Chrysotus tricaudatus sp. nov. D-G: Chrysotus komovi sp. nov. H – J: Chrysotus albibarbus Loew. K – N: Chrysotus obscuripes Zetterstedt. A, D, H, K: Hypopygium, lateral view. B, E: Antenna, lateral view. C, G, L: Tip of phallus, dorsal view. F, I, M: Phallus, lateral view. J, N: Surstylus, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/230258/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

